 244:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_i2c.c ****       (+) __HAL_I2C_DISABLE: Disable the I2C peripheral
 245:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_i2c.c ****       (+) __HAL_I2C_GENERATE_NACK: Generate a Non-Acknowledge I2C peripheral in Slave mode
