1059:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_i2c.c ****             dedicated I2C IRQ when using Interrupt mode or the DMA IRQ when
1060:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_i2c.c ****             using DMA mode.
